        <title>Offshore Wind Turbine Condition Monitoring and Maintenance Strategy Optimization: A Cost-Effectiveness Based Decision Framework</title>
        <link>https://whhong-research.github.io/en/p/offshore-wind-turbine-condition-monitoring-and-maintenance-strategy-optimization-a-cost-effectiveness-based-decision-framework/</link>
