		data-flex-basis=&#34;445px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;other-assumptions&#34;&gt;Other Assumptions
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Parameter&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Setting&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Wind Turbine Service Life&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;20 years&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Standard design life&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Post-repair State&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&amp;ldquo;as good as new&amp;rdquo;&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Complete repair assumption&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;om-strategy-system&#34;&gt;O&amp;amp;M Strategy System
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-corrective-maintenance&#34;&gt;1. Corrective Maintenance
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Definition&lt;/strong&gt;: Maintenance performed after a substructure has completely failed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Characteristics&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passive responsive maintenance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Usually highest cost (including downtime losses and emergency repair costs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Suitable for non-critical components or situations where failure consequences are not serious&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-time-based-maintenance&#34;&gt;2. Time-Based Maintenance
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Definition&lt;/strong&gt;: Maintenance performed according to predetermined time intervals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Classification&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Basic Service (BS)&lt;/strong&gt;: Discover and fix common, easy-to-repair but difficult-to-monitor problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Service (AS)&lt;/strong&gt;: Comprehensive inspection of all structural components&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimization Direction&lt;/strong&gt;: Shortening the time interval between adjacent AS can improve wind turbine availability, but is still not as effective as using a monitoring system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;3-condition-based-maintenance-cbm&#34;&gt;3. Condition-Based Maintenance (CBM)
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Definition&lt;/strong&gt;: Maintenance based on the actual health state of the wind turbine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Elements&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relies on CMS fault detection capability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Real-time assessment of equipment health status&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intervention before failure occurs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Effectiveness&lt;/strong&gt;: Depends on CMS detection accuracy, response speed, and timeliness of maintenance decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;maintenance-framework-system&#34;&gt;Maintenance Framework System
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The research defines three maintenance levels:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Maintenance Level&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Corresponding Fault Type&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Maintenance Content&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Maintenance 1&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Minor Fault&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Repair minor defects, prevent deterioration&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Maintenance 2&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Critical Fault&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Repair serious defects, restore function&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Maintenance 3&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Complete Failure&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Comprehensive repair or component replacement&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%8A%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/image-20250303160352843.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1376&#34;
	height=&#34;824&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%8A%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/image-20250303160352843_hu_d74ad046dee78bd1.png 480w, https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%8A%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/image-20250303160352843_hu_51a1a938e8222f16.png 1024w&#34;
