		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;437&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1050px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;four-monitoring-system-configurations&#34;&gt;Four Monitoring System Configurations
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Configuration&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Characteristics&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;No Monitoring System&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Only relies on periodic inspections and post-failure repairs&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Lowest cost, but highest risk&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;SCADA&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Utilizes existing wind turbine monitoring and data acquisition systems&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Low cost, but limited detection capability&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;CMS&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Dedicated condition monitoring system&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Strong detection capability, but higher cost&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;SCADA+CMS&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Two systems working synergistically&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Comprehensive advantages, strongest detection capability&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;degradation-and-detection-models&#34;&gt;Degradation and Detection Models
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;system-degradation-model-architecture&#34;&gt;System Degradation Model Architecture
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The research adopts &lt;strong&gt;Petri Nets&lt;/strong&gt; to model the system degradation process:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%8A%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%9B%91%E6%B5%8B%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/image-20250303160707353.png&#34;
