&lt;h2 id=&#34;maintenance-process&#34;&gt;Maintenance Process
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Time node definitions in the maintenance process:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Phase&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Code&lt;/th&gt;
          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/thead&gt;
  &lt;tbody&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Fault Detection to Repair Order&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;M1&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Time from fault detection to repair order issuance&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Maintenance Planning Meeting&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;M2&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Time to arrange meeting to formulate maintenance plan&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Plan Formulation&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;M3&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Time to formulate detailed maintenance plan&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Resource Preparation&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;M4+M5&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Time to charter vessel, dispatch personnel, prepare maintenance equipment&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Spare Parts Call&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;M6&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Time to activate spare parts if available (much shorter than M5)&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Departure Preparation&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;M7&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Maintenance vessel preparation for departure&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Transport to Site&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;M8/M9&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Time for transport vessel to reach site, M9 considers weather factors (waiting for suitable weather window)&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Maintenance Implementation&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;M11&lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Time required for maintenance operations&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
